---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-200 mt-auto">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
          <img src="/vietnam-logo.ico" alt="Vietnam Logo" class="w-6 h-6" />
          <span class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-900">AnkiVN</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Bộ sưu tập deck Anki, hướng dẫn và bài viết học tập cho cộng đồng Việt Nam.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Links -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Nội dung</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/decks" class="text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Bộ thẻ</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides" class="text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Hướng dẫn</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog" class="text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="/submit" class="text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Gửi deck</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div class="md:col-span-1">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Liên hệ</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/about" class="text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Giới thiệu</a></li>
          <li><a href="mailto:hello@ankivn.com" class="text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Email</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/ankivn" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">GitHub</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom -->
    <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          © {currentYear} AnkiVN. Nội dung được chia sẻ theo giấy phép 
          <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-blue-600">CC BY-NC</a>.
        </p>
        <div class="flex space-x-6 mt-4 md:mt-0">
          <a href="/privacy" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Quyền riêng tư</a>
          <a href="/terms" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Điều khoản</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
